[SN]TITLE[SN]
Alcohol units guide

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A report by a group of MPs has expressed concern that government guidelines on how much alcohol people should drink "appeared to endorse daily drinking". Here we show what the government recommends and what the units actually mean (some percentages are rounded up to the nearest whole figure).

